		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />His second album "Color Caves" is out now too. It shows full screen graphics.
<br />
<br />You know, I thought these would be longer songs, since it costs as much as an album.  However, they are rather short, in typical NES style.  They're cool tunes and all, but I thought we'd get some longer tracks like the intro to Solstice, which clocks at about 3 minutes, iirc.
<br />
<br />-Rob

		

